Specifically, the ITSM domain schema, seed databases, and tool surface (action
space) in this project are a port/derivative of that project's ITSM environment.
The conversational multi-turn user-simulator and the multi-tenancy (org-scoped /
MSP) model are original to this project; the verification format (state-based DB
comparison + natural-language assertions) follows the style of tau-bench (Yao et
al., arXiv:2406.12045).

